node.text:
Y’all.. pre-order my new book at magnolia.com for a chance to win a $1,000 check PLUS a weekend in Waco to experience all things Magnolia. 

Legal stuff 🤓 No purchase necessary. Must be U.S. resident, 18 or older. Starts 3/1/21 at 12:01 a.m. CT and ends 3/5/21 at 11:59 p.m. CT. To enter without pre-ordering a book, visit https://magnolia.com/no-pain-no-gaines-giveaway & complete the entry form. Travel is not included. Limit 1 entry per person. Void where prohibited. Additional terms, conditions & restrictions apply. For complete details, see https://magnolia.com/no-pain-no-gaines-giveaway-rules

node.text: Everybody knows.. #fixerUpper is where we’ve been and @magnolianetwork is where we’re going! But what if we tied both together as a tribute to this new journey—for old times’ sake. Fixer Upper: meet Magnolia Network. Magnolia Network: meet Fixer Upper! Feels pretty good to me..

node.text: WHHAATT! @magnolianetwork is here and we just flat out can’t believe it.. Thanks for being with us through all of these incredible once in a lifetime experiences! node.text: When I think of Gabe, I feel compelled to run. So I’ll do just that today in honor of 2 years since her passing 💙 She said, “It’s okay to struggle. It’s not okay to give up.” Thinking of @justingrunewald1 and all of you who have been changed by her powerful legacy. We love you, Gabe!

Y’all.. pre-order my new book at magnolia.com for a chance to win a $1,000 check PLUS a weekend in Waco to experience all things Magnolia. 

Legal stuff 🤓 No purchase necessary. Must be U.S. resident, 18 or older. Starts 3/1/21 at 12:01 a.m. CT and ends 3/5/21 at 11:59 p.m. CT. To enter without pre-ordering a book, visit https://magnolia.com/no-pain-no-gaines-giveaway & complete the entry form. Travel is not included. Limit 1 entry per person. Void where prohibited.
